a Elias","date":"April 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThis grandson of mine is a master. Perhaps Allah will reconcile two groups of Muslims through him.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2557 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20383,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/02\/17\/hasan-ali-ibn-abi-talib\/","url_meta":{"origin":3927,"position":4},"title":"Hasan on Ali: Hasan descreibes virtues of Ali ibn Abi Talib","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 17, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn Hubshi reported: Hasan ibn Ali addressed the people after the killing of Ali ibn Abi Talib and he said, \u201cA man has departed you yesterday whom none from the early generation could surpass in knowledge and none from the later generation will match him. If the Messenger of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33256,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2